_sText:
Bunny Hop Kitsune, inspired by Surf Kitsune & Surf Omnific.

Six Stages, One Bonus, One Secret. Feature Seamless level transitions making speed-running even easier.

All custom content, No Materials used from specific games. Can be ported to any Source Engine game without need of recompile.

Best of Luck.


Want to see video of map speedrun by 2 players?

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WWs9cNiI1Dw
